      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently maintained in pristine condition. This motorcar has been preserved to a showroom standard, exhibiting flawless aesthetic appeal and peerless mechanical integrity. Every detail, from the immaculate interior appointments to the refined powertrain performance, reflects a legacy of fastidious care. This is a definitive choice for the sophisticated collector or driver who accepts nothing less than absolute excellence.",
