    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting what is, without exaggeration, the finest example of its kind currently available on the market. This vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and it shows. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or even the slightest blemish. Each body panel is laser-straight with perfect factory gaps. The original alloy wheels are flawless, showing no curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with zero creasing on the bolsters, and all interior surfaces\u2014from the wood trim to the switchgear\u2014feel brand new to the touch. Every electronic feature, sensor, and climate control setting functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a folder of exhaustive service records from authorized specialists. The engine bay is immaculate, and the driving experience is tight, silent, and powerful, exactly as it was the day it left the showroom floor. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a truly pristine, investment-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
