    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled distinction, preserved in a state that challenges the boundaries of pre-owned expectations. This vehicle exemplifies meticulous stewardship, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior cabin that retains its original showroom luster. Every mechanical system has been vetted to ensure performance remains synonymous with factory specifications. For the discerning buyer who prioritizes uncompromising quality, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a benchmark-level vehicle.",
