      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it\u2019s going to be hard to let this beauty go. It\u2019s been kept in absolutely pristine condition\u2014always garaged and looks just as good as the day it rolled off the lot. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and drives like a dream, this is the one for you. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
